jalds.alds.ds.tree.rb
Class RedBlackNode

java.lang.Object
  jalds.alds.ds.tree.rb.RedBlackNode

public class RedBlackNode
extends java.lang.Object

A Red Black Node is extends a regular tree node and add one extra bit of storage the color of the node.The users will probably never have to use this class directly.

Author:
Devender Gollapally
